---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Services"
  description="Custom WordPress builds, Next.js/Astro development, and website maintenance. Free quote within 48h from an independent developer."
  pageKey="services"
>
  <section class="pt-28 pb-20 sm:pb-28 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div
        class="border border-vert/20 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-surface shadow-sm"
        data-reveal
      >
        <!-- Terminal title bar -->
        <div
          class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 sm:px-5 py-3 border-b border-vert/10 bg-surface-alt"
        >
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ff5f56]"></span>
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ffbd2e]"></span>
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#28c840]"></span>
          <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-ink/70 font-medium"
            >olivier@otvt:~/services</span
          >
        </div>
        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="px-6 sm:px-12 py-8 sm:py-14">
          <p
            class="text-xs text-vert/85 font-mono mb-8 sm:mb-10 leading-relaxed"
          >
            <span class="text-vert font-semibold">olivier@otvt</span>:<span
              class="text-jaune">~</span
            ><span class="text-ink/70">$ </span><span
              class="text-ink/70" data-typewriter>cat services.txt</span
            >
          </p>
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-12 sm:gap-16">
            <div class="sm:col-span-1">
              <p
                class="text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.15em] text-vert/85 uppercase"
              >
                Services
              </p>
              <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-ink">
                What I offer
              </h1>
              <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-ink/70 leading-relaxed">
                From simple showcase sites to complex applications, every
                project is unique.
              </p>
              <a
                href="/en/contact"
                class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-vert text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-vert/90 transition-all duration-200"
              >
                Get started
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  width="14"
                  height="14"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  ><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"
                  ></path></svg
                >
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="sm:col-span-2 space-y-10">
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">WordPress</h2>
                <p
                  class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink/70 leading-relaxed max-w-lg"
                >
                  Custom themes, WooCommerce, plugins. I build every site from
                  scratch, no pre-made templates. Tailored design, optimized
                  performance.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >Custom themes</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >WooCommerce</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >Performance</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">
                  Custom development
                </h2>
                <p
                  class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink/70 leading-relaxed max-w-lg"
                >
                  From lightning-fast showcase sites to complex applications,
                  built from scratch around your needs. Clean code, built to
                  last and easy to grow.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >Tailored</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >Fast</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >Scalable</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">
                  Maintenance & upgrades
                </h2>
                <p
                  class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink/70 leading-relaxed max-w-lg"
                >
                  Technical audits, security updates, performance
                  improvements. I also take over existing sites to
                  modernize them.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >Audit & security</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >Migration</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >Performance</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <section class="pb-20 sm:pb-28 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div
        class="border border-vert/20 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-surface shadow-sm"
        data-reveal
      >
        <div
          class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 sm:px-5 py-3 border-b border-vert/10 bg-surface-alt"
        >
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ff5f56]"></span>
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ffbd2e]"></span>
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#28c840]"></span>
          <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-ink/70 font-medium"
            >olivier@otvt:~/methodology</span
          >
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 sm:px-12 py-8 sm:py-14">
          <p
            class="text-xs text-vert/85 font-mono mb-8 sm:mb-10 leading-relaxed"
          >
            <span class="text-vert font-semibold">olivier@otvt</span>:<span
              class="text-jaune">~</span
            ><span class="text-ink/70">$ </span><span
              class="text-ink/70" data-typewriter>cat process.sh</span
            >
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.15em] text-vert/85 uppercase mb-6"
          >
            Process
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-ink">
            How I work
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-ink/70 leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
            Transparency, fast iterations and quality. A simple, effective
            process.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-12 grid sm:grid-cols-4 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <span
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-vert/10 text-vert text-lg font-bold mb-4"
                >01</span
              >
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink">Discovery</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-ink/70 leading-relaxed">
                Analysis of your needs, goals and constraints. A clear brief
                to start on solid ground.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <span
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-jaune/20 text-amber-ink text-lg font-bold mb-4"
                >02</span
              >
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink">Design</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-ink/70 leading-relaxed">
                Mockups, validation and technical architecture. You approve
                every step before development starts.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <span
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-vert/10 text-vert text-lg font-bold mb-4"
                >03</span
              >
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink">
                Development
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-ink/70 leading-relaxed">
                Short iterations, continuous testing. You follow progress in
                real time and give feedback along the way.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <span
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-jaune/20 text-amber-ink text-lg font-bold mb-4"
                >04</span
              >
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink">Launch</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-ink/70 leading-relaxed">
                Going live, handover and follow-up. I stay available after
                delivery for peace of mind.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <!-- Backdrop overlay -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-bg opacity-60"></div>
      <div class="relative max-w-xl mx-auto">
        <div
          class="border border-vert/25 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-surface shadow-lg shadow-vert/5"
          data-reveal
        >
          <!-- Title bar -->
          <div
            class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 sm:px-5 py-3 border-b border-vert/10 bg-surface-alt"
          >
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ff5f56]"></span>
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ffbd2e]"></span>
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#28c840]"></span>
            <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-ink/70 font-medium"
              >olivier@otvt:~/call</span
            >
          </div>
          <!-- Content -->
          <div class="px-6 sm:px-10 py-8 sm:py-10 text-center">
            <p class="text-xs text-vert/85 font-mono mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              <span class="text-vert font-semibold">olivier@otvt</span>:<span
                class="text-jaune">~</span
              ><span class="text-ink/70">$ </span><span
                class="text-ink/70" data-typewriter>./call-to-action.sh</span
              >
            </p>
            <span
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-vert/10 text-vert mb-5"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path
                  d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"
                ></path></svg
              >
            </span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-ink">
              Not sure where to start?
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-ink/70">
              Let's talk for 30 minutes, no strings attached.
            </p>
            <a
              href="/en/contact"
              class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-vert text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-vert/90 transition-all duration-200 shadow-sm"
            >
              Book a call
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="14"
                height="14"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg
              >
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
